        }
      ],
      "body": "Implies(And(A**2 * (1 - s)**2 == (2 * p * A * B - p**2 * (A**2 + B**2)) * s**2, B**2 * (1 - t)**2 == (2 * p * A * B - p**2 * (A**2 + B**2)) * t**2), (B * s * (1 - t))**2 == (A * t * (1 - s))**2)"
    },
    {
      "name": "cramer_intersection_parameters",
      "english": "Solving the two line-parameter equations for M on BK and AL gives u(s+t-st)=t and v(s+t-st)=s, provided the determinant is nonzero.",
